[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 7437,
        "end_time": 12818,
        "text": "Without water, a human can only\nsurvive for about 100 hours."
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 12818,
        "end_time": 18148,
        "text": "But there&#39;s a creature so resilient\nthat it can go without it for decades."
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 18148,
        "end_time": 21458,
        "text": "This one millimeter animal can survive\nboth the hottest"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 21458,
        "end_time": 24708,
        "text": "and coldest environments on Earth,"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 24708,
        "end_time": 28519,
        "text": "and can even withstand high levels\nof radiation."
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 28519,
        "end_time": 30420,
        "text": "This is the tardigrade,"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 30420,
        "end_time": 33289,
        "text": "and it&#39;s one of the toughest creatures\non Earth,"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 33289,
        "end_time": 38049,
        "text": "even if it does look more like\na chubby, eight-legged gummy bear."
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 38049,
        "end_time": 40749,
        "text": "Most organisms need water to survive."
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 40749,
        "end_time": 43059,
        "text": "Water allows metabolism to occur,"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 43059,
        "end_time": 46080,
        "text": "which is the process that drives\nall the biochemical reactions"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 46080,
        "end_time": 49249,
        "text": "that take place in cells."
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 49249,
        "end_time": 53409,
        "text": "But creatures like the tardigrade,\nalso known as the water bear,"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 53409,
        "end_time": 58069,
        "text": "get around this restriction\nwith a process called anhydrobiosis,"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 58069,
        "end_time": 61100,
        "text": "from the Greek meaning\nlife without water."
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 61100,
        "end_time": 64728,
        "text": "And however extraordinary,\ntardigrades aren&#39;t alone."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 64728,
        "end_time": 65780,
        "text": "Bacteria,"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 65780,
        "end_time": 68309,
        "text": "single-celled organisms called archaea,"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 68309,
        "end_time": 69090,
        "text": "plants,"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 69090,
        "end_time": 73269,
        "text": "and even other animals \ncan all survive drying up."
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 73269,
        "end_time": 74671,
        "text": "For many tardigrades,"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 74671,
        "end_time": 78571,
        "text": "this requires that they go through \nsomething called a tun state."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 78571,
        "end_time": 80030,
        "text": "They curl up into a ball,"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 80030,
        "end_time": 83620,
        "text": "pulling their head and eight legs\ninside their body"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 83620,
        "end_time": 87000,
        "text": "and wait until water returns."
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 87000,
        "end_time": 89141,
        "text": "It&#39;s thought that as water\nbecomes scarce"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 89141,
        "end_time": 91501,
        "text": "and tardigrades enter their tun state,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 91501,
        "end_time": 94351,
        "text": "they start synthesize special molecules,"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 94351,
        "end_time": 98041,
        "text": "which fill the tardigrade&#39;s cells\nto replace lost water"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 98041,
        "end_time": 100430,
        "text": "by forming a matrix."
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 100430,
        "end_time": 103080,
        "text": "Components of the cells that are\nsensitive to dryness,"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 103080,
        "end_time": 104111,
        "text": "like DNA,"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 104111,
        "end_time": 105101,
        "text": "proteins,"
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 105101,
        "end_time": 106191,
        "text": "and membranes,"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 106191,
        "end_time": 108580,
        "text": "get trapped in this matrix."
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 108580,
        "end_time": 111973,
        "text": "It&#39;s thought that this keeps these\nmolecules locked in position"
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 111973,
        "end_time": 113631,
        "text": "to stop them from unfolding,"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 113631,
        "end_time": 114868,
        "text": "breaking apart,"
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 114868,
        "end_time": 116931,
        "text": "or fusing together."
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 116931,
        "end_time": 120421,
        "text": "Once the organism is rehydrated,\nthe matrix dissolves,"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 120421,
        "end_time": 123887,
        "text": "leaving behind undamaged, \nfunctional cells."
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 123887,
        "end_time": 128151,
        "text": "Beyond dryness, tardigrades can also\ntolerate other extreme stresses:"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 128151,
        "end_time": 129416,
        "text": "being frozen,"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 129416,
        "end_time": 131830,
        "text": "heated up past the boiling point\nof water,"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 131830,
        "end_time": 133507,
        "text": "high levels of radiation,"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 133507,
        "end_time": 137092,
        "text": "and even the vacuum of outer space."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 137092,
        "end_time": 139221,
        "text": "This has led to some erroneous speculation"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 139221,
        "end_time": 142562,
        "text": "that tardigrades \nare extraterrestrial beings."
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 142562,
        "end_time": 144150,
        "text": "While that&#39;s fun to think about,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 144150,
        "end_time": 147751,
        "text": "scientific evidence places their\norigin firmly on Earth"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 147751,
        "end_time": 149772,
        "text": "where they&#39;ve evolved over time."
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 149772,
        "end_time": 152503,
        "text": "In fact, this earthly evolution \nhas given rise"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 152503,
        "end_time": 156322,
        "text": "to over 1100 known species of tardigrades"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 156322,
        "end_time": 159653,
        "text": "and there are probably many others\nyet to be discovered."
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 159653,
        "end_time": 164783,
        "text": "And because tardigrades are so hardy,\nthey exist just about everywhere."
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 164783,
        "end_time": 168463,
        "text": "They live on every continent,\nincluding Antarctica."
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 168463,
        "end_time": 171152,
        "text": "And they&#39;re in diverse biomes\nincluding deserts,"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 171152,
        "end_time": 172283,
        "text": "ice sheets,"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 172283,
        "end_time": 173182,
        "text": "the sea,"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 173182,
        "end_time": 174143,
        "text": "fresh water,"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 174143,
        "end_time": 175233,
        "text": "rainforests,"
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 175233,
        "end_time": 177242,
        "text": "and the highest mountain peaks."
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 177242,
        "end_time": 180913,
        "text": "But you can find tardigrades\nin the most ordinary places, too,"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 180913,
        "end_time": 182904,
        "text": "like moss or lichen found in yards,"
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 182904,
        "end_time": 183693,
        "text": "parks,"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 183693,
        "end_time": 184963,
        "text": "and forests."
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 184963,
        "end_time": 188403,
        "text": "All you need to find them is a little\npatience and a microscope."
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 188403,
        "end_time": 192323,
        "text": "Scientists are now to trying to find out\nwhether tardigrades use the tun state,"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 192323,
        "end_time": 194364,
        "text": "their anti-drying technique,"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 194364,
        "end_time": 196293,
        "text": "to survive other stresses."
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 196293,
        "end_time": 198683,
        "text": "If we can understand how they,\nand other creatures,"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 198683,
        "end_time": 201852,
        "text": "stabilize their sensitive \nbiological molecules,"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 201852,
        "end_time": 206043,
        "text": "perhaps we could apply this knowledge\nto help us stabilize vaccines,"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 206043,
        "end_time": 211793,
        "text": "or to develop stress-tolerant crops that \ncan cope with Earth&#39;s changing climate."
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 211793,
        "end_time": 214214,
        "text": "And by studying how tardigrades survive"
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 214214,
        "end_time": 217373,
        "text": "prolonged exposure \nto the vacuum of outer space,"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 217373,
        "end_time": 222195,
        "text": "scientists can generate clues about\nthe environmental limits of life"
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 222195,
        "end_time": 224205,
        "text": "and how to safeguard astronauts."
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 224205,
        "end_time": 229164,
        "text": "In the process, tardigrades could even\nhelp us answer a critical question:"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 229164,
        "end_time": 233923,
        "text": "could life survive on planets much\nless hospitable than our own?"
    }
]